{
  "stem": "20142.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a young set of-- they used to call him Benny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very well dressed with high boots and, you know, breeches, riding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very nicely made up tunic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody was wondering, what's-- why is Benny so well liked, and what is he doing over here?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, Benny is one of the guys who were told to hang his father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I will never forget this, that I couldn't understand how a child could do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But evidently he done it, because many people were saying, if I ever lived the war-- over the war, I would find him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And let's see what he can do about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't know if he had any sadistical tendency or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he didn't bother anybody or denounce anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He were just like a puppet then of a field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sometime in-- at the age of 13, he had cigarettes in his pocket, and he was-- would have lit up one cigarette and then threw it away so somebody could pick it up.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a trick for the Germans to see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they picked him up and beat the blue daylight out of the-- if anybody picked up the pot that Benny threw away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] these procedures existed on the normal condition.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the morning hours, they took us out of barracks at 4 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Rain, shine, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At 6 o'clock, we had to be ready to march out to some kind of work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Most of the work was done building roads around the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were either rollers engage, or shovel and little wagons to bring earth from place to place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It sometime looked like something was done without any purpose.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
